item.title: How can i turn a rs2 lvl 33 into a lvl 80 in 1month
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Ok, because you say it’s a pure, I assume you’ve only trained range and magic, if so, get 27 attack then do vampire slayer, that will get you either 31 or 32, from there, get an addy scimmy and train strength to mid 50’s up to 60, then focus either on getting 40 attack then 40 defense, or just get defense/strength as high as you can.

Also, bury any bones from training, suggested to use hill giants until 25-30 prayer. Also, lets say you’ve just reached 55 strength with 32 attack, use strength pots. Also, do Dragon Slayer as soon as you can.
